---
title: Lemon-Pepper Pork Schnitzel & Apple Salad with Creamy Roast Potato & Beetroot Relish
description: We’re putting a pep in this pork schnitzel’s step by adding some lemon and pepper seasoning to the golden panko crumb.
it will zap through the crunch, serve with creamy roast baby potatoes to really make this dish fun. You’ll be skipping to the
dinner table in anticipation.
